{"tid":1466493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"極緊急!! 其實做錯又點，唔需要氣餒，大家學下林鄭既做法 就知我地仲有得贏，請廣傳!!!","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:51.000Z","uid":204047,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f63830abce5a3ed47147afc047e619816435ba9","tid":1466493,"uid":204047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"請大家聽聽我講，我出過好多次 亦上過前線，太多手足 覺得做錯一次就輸哂，千萬唔好咁唸 你只會俾人分化，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭到今時今日仲可以若無其事行出黎就係因為佢從來對佢做既事都採取一個若無其事既態度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，錯係要檢討但我地照樣聽日照塞機場，過一兩日就會無人記得今日發生既事 我地繼續5大訴求先係重中之重，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你為今日既事去割去感到絕望就中正林鄭圈套!!</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"db0eba507f09761a9b878564a7c8ea58e30db2e6","tid":1466493,"uid":204047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbcd4699839722e21de282c3754f9254d89864d2","tid":1466493,"uid":204047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a83f0427e37b50887693919028229b9861f4f73","tid":1466493,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65711c1e3675fa162e293936c19a7428a60c0c24","tid":1466493,"uid":188432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"(集思廣益長文) 求大家用2分鐘時間睇睇 解決問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7bd900d978672ec2e865e533c41ace5903033f53","tid":1466493,"uid":188432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb101be0fc8b517ddd90417f8efffa01d6193cbc","tid":1466493,"uid":117361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼"},{"pid":"b289e0a10fe4b5d376de2878a008